Global Knit Underwear and Nightwear Market Insights
Knit Underwear and Nightwear Market size was valued at USD 32.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 45.8 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 5.2% from 2024 to 2030.


Knit Underwear and Nightwear Market Overview
The global Knit Underwear and Nightwear market was valued at USD 18.42 billion in 2024 and is expected to reach USD 23.68 billion by 2032, growing at a CAGR of 3.1% during the forecast period. This market is driven by the increasing demand for comfortable and breathable fabric for sleepwear and intimate wear. The market is witnessing a shift towards sustainable materials, with several manufacturers focusing on eco-friendly production methods. Additionally, innovations in design and fabric technology are attracting more consumers towards premium, high-performance products.

